trans-unit.source:
\n

Specifies the default value for a property.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx xxx x xxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An 8-bit unsigned integer that is the default value.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx 0$xxx xxxxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

A Unicode character that is the default value.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X Xxxxxxx xxxxxxxxx xxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

A double-precision floating point number that is the default value.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxx$xxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxx xxxxxx xxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

A 16-bit signed integer that is the default value.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X 00$xxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

A 32-bit signed integer that is the default value.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X 00$xxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

A 64-bit signed integer that is the default value.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X 00$xxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

A single-precision floating point number that is the default value.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxx$xxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxx xxxxxx xxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

Gets the default value of the property this attribute is bound to.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx xx xxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxx xx xxxxx xx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

The object to test the value equality of.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxx xxxxxx xx xxxx xxx xxxxx xxxxxxxx xx.

trans-unit.source: true if the value of the given object is equal to that of the current; otherwise, false.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$$x$xxxxxx$xxxx$$xxxxxx$ xx xxx xxxxx xx xxx xxxxx xxxxxx xx xxxxx xx xxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx$ xxxxxxxxx$ $xxxxxx$xxxxx$$xxxxxx$.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Returns the hash code for this instance.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxx xxx xxxx xxxx xxx xxxx xxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A 32-bit signed integer hash code.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X 00$xxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxxx.$$x$$x
